			<div class="dablink">This article is about the Korean civilization. For the modern political entities, see <a href="/wiki/North_Korea" title="North Korea">North Korea</a> and <a href="/wiki/South_Korea" title="South Korea">South Korea</a>. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Korea_(disambiguation)" title="Korea (disambiguation)">Korea (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
