<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFDelmer_M._Brown_.28ed..291993">Delmer M. Brown (ed.), ed (1993). <i><a href="http://books.google.com/books?visbn=0521223520&amp;id=x5mwgfPXK1kC&amp;pg=PA159&amp;lpg=PA159&amp;vq=buddhism&amp;dq=Paekche+hostage+japan&amp;sig=dwsfsmf80GCVdVXe90a5s9Tkq34" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?visbn=0521223520&amp;id=x5mwgfPXK1kC&amp;pg=PA159&amp;lpg=PA159&amp;vq=buddhism&amp;dq=Paekche+hostage+japan&amp;sig=dwsfsmf80GCVdVXe90a5s9Tkq34" rel="nofollow">The Cambridge History of Japan</a></i>. Cambridge University Press. pp.&#160;140–149<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?visbn=0521223520&amp;id=x5mwgfPXK1kC&amp;pg=PA159&amp;lpg=PA159&amp;vq=buddhism&amp;dq=Paekche+hostage+japan&amp;sig=dwsfsmf80GCVdVXe90a5s9Tkq34" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?visbn=0521223520&amp;id=x5mwgfPXK1kC&amp;pg=PA159&amp;lpg=PA159&amp;vq=buddhism&amp;dq=Paekche+hostage+japan&amp;sig=dwsfsmf80GCVdVXe90a5s9Tkq34" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?visbn=0521223520&amp;id=x5mwgfPXK1kC&amp;pg=PA159&amp;lpg=PA159&amp;vq=buddhism&amp;dq=Paekche+hostage+japan&amp;sig=dwsfsmf80GCVdVXe90a5s9Tkq34</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Cambridge+History+of+Japan&amp;rft.date=1993&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B140%E2%80%93149&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fvisbn%3D0521223520%26id%3Dx5mwgfPXK1kC%26pg%3DPA159%26lpg%3DPA159%26vq%3Dbuddhism%26dq%3DPaekche%2Bhostage%2Bjapan%26sig%3Ddwsfsmf80GCVdVXe90a5s9Tkq34&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Korea"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>; George Sansom, <i>A History of Japan to 1334</i>, Stanford University Press, 1958. p. 47. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0804705232" 